{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7c15864eb9","title":"本卷说明","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c4d6adaa18","index":0,"year":2017,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"7c15864eb9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","name":"斯大林选集（诸夏怀斯社2017年5月）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"斯大林，诸夏怀斯社2017年5月","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"e43ce1051b","name":"诸夏怀斯社"}]},"publication_details":{"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a3a559def8","type":"paragraph","text":"本卷说明","index":0,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9"},{"id":"d70ce9b92d","type":"paragraph","text":"新编《斯大林选集》共分四卷，是根据新编《斯大林全集》正卷十卷和档案附卷十卷编辑的。各卷内容的起说时间为：第一卷，一九O一年至一九二四年；第二卷，一九二五年至一九二八年；第三卷，一九二九年至一九四〇年；第四卷，一九四一年至一九五三年。","index":1,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9"},{"id":"0bdc922063","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七九年出版的原《斯大林选集》，仅为两卷，按照当时的政治、理论需要，剔除了斯大林关于阶级斗争、工人运动、暴力革命、论反对派、卫国战争，以及中国革命等方面的大量文献。现新编《斯大林选集》已尽可能予以增补、充实，以力求全面地反映这位历更伟人和革命导师的思想、理论和非凡经历","index":2,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9"},{"id":"894e638bec","type":"paragraph","text":"近年来陆续解密的苏联历史档案中，有众多关于斯大林的档案材料，新编《斯大林选集》亦摄要单独编辑成“斯大林历史档案选”，作为附卷附于第四卷之后，供读者参考。第四卷之后还附有新编《斯大林全集》正卷二十卷总目录和档案附卷十卷总目录的下载地址","index":3,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9"},{"id":"45d1f334ef","type":"paragraph","text":"本选集中的日期，在一九一八年二月十四日之前都依旧历（正教历），其后为公历。","index":4,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9"},{"id":"2b7a43d65d","type":"paragraph","text":"本选集中的注释，一为原书著者（斯大林）注，二为译者注，三为编者注，均用圆形注码（①、②、③.·..··）标明，释文置于当页末；正文中原加着重号的文字，在本选集中均用黑体字标示","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9"},{"id":"830d1f00d1","type":"paragraph","text":"本选集中的部分篇目标题，是我们拟加的。","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9"},{"id":"95e9e04a6a","type":"paragraph","text":"本选集文字虽经多次校对，错论之处仍恐难免，希读者指正","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9"},{"id":"93ec0eeb34","type":"paragraph","text":"本书编者诸息怀斯社","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9"},{"id":"7cc8cc6cb4","type":"paragraph","text":"hqxsk@163.com","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9"},{"id":"b38abcbb2c","type":"paragraph","text":"联系邮箱","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9"}],"page":{"id":"40ad140d61","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"7c15864eb9","start":47,"end":47}}}},"__N_SSG":true}